[src:commander-cli/commander-js] Long descriptions are wrapped to fit the available width.
[src:commander-cli/commander-js] You can add extra text to be displayed along with the built-in help.
[src:commander-cli/commander-js] The positions "beforeAll" and "afterAll" apply to the command and all its subcommands.
[src:commander-cli/commander-js] The second parameter can be a string, or a function returning a string.
