[src:commander-cli/commander-js] The default behaviour for usage errors is to just display a short error message.
[src:commander-cli/commander-js] You can change the behaviour to show the full help or a custom help message after an error.
[src:commander-cli/commander-js] The default behaviour is to suggest correct spelling after an error for an unknown command or option.
[src:commander-cli/commander-js] `.help()`: display help information and exit immediately.
