[src:commander-cli/commander-js] This allows you to customise the usage description in the first line of the help.
[src:commander-cli/commander-js] The description appears in the help for the command.
[src:commander-cli/commander-js] You can optionally supply a shorter summary to use when listed as a subcommand of the program.
[src:commander-cli/commander-js] By default, every command has a help option.
[src:commander-cli/commander-js] You may change the default help flags and description.
